\doxysubsection{Detailed Description}
Zero offset CRS parameter inversion (RN, RNIP, BETA) with Very Fast Simulated Aneeling (VFSA) Global Optimization. 

This program uses the Non-\/\+Hyperbolic CRS approximation to fit data cube and get the parameters (Fomel, 2013).

Programer\+: Rodolfo A. C. Neves (Dirack) 19/09/2019

Site\+: \href{https://dirack.github.io}{\texttt{ https\+://dirack.\+github.\+io}}

